=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">We got a glimpse of <em>Playoff Tom Brady<=
/em> yesterday as the
GOAT delivered his strongest performance to date in the broadcast booth. Br=
ady <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2=
UktxclJLZ0dVWW1Ebk9KLU9sdmlyREl3N1gyND0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly94LmNvbS9hd2Z=
1bGFubm91bmNpbmcvc3RhdHVzLzE4Nzg1NzM5NjkwMTc4MzU3NTk_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPVRoZS=
