<strong>Randy Levine</strong> are close to <strong>Donald Trump</strong>, l=
eading to some speculation that they can tap into the incoming president=E2=
=80=99s deep well of animosity toward MSNBC=E2=80=99s former owner to help =
get a deal done.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin:0;">To this day, Comcast executives insist that they didn=E2=
